name: Aaliyah Thompson
summary:
Aaliyah Thompson, aged 28, is a Film Producer in the entertainment industry based in Los Angeles. Originally from Brooklyn, New York, Aaliyah is a graduate from New York University who values loyalty, ambition, and creativity. She is a fluent speaker of English and Spanish, who interests in cinema, photography, traveling, and yoga. 

Aaliyah describes herself as spiritual and liberal politically. She is seeking a long-term monogamous relationship. She identifies as a straight woman and uses the pronouns She/Her/Hers. She belongs to the Black African descent. 

Aaliyah does not currently have children but does wish to have them in the future. She is a dog owner, occasionally drinks but doesn't use any kind of drugs nor smokes. She enjoys maintaining an active lifestyle. 

As far as her partner preferences go, she is interested in straight men aged between 28 to 38, who are at least 5'10" tall. They should enjoy an active lifestyle, want children in the future, comfortable with drinking but avoid smoking or drug use.
